                    <li><strong>Daily Deposit Limit:</strong> {{dailyDepositLimit}} RWF (previously {{previousDailyDeposit}} RWF)</li>
                    <li><strong>Interest Rate:</strong> {{interestRate}}% p.a. (previously {{previousInterestRate}}%)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

