                â€¢ Special promotional offers
            </p>

            <p>Thank you for being a valued member of Credit Jambo. We look forward to continuing to serve your financial needs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Credit Jambo Ltd</strong></p>
            <p>Growing together towards financial success</p>
